CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 23, 1951, pg. 32 reads: "Grads Of The College, Soldiers, Teachers - Left photo: George Barbour, James C. Gohanna and James J. Robinson were graduated form the college at Pitt."
TitMainTitle: University of Pittsburgh graduates, from left: George Barbour, James C. Gohanna, and James J. "Jimmy Joe" Robinson, posed in front of Syria Mosque, Oakland
